Bot needs the following permissions in Guild/Server-->
1.`Send Messages` : This is given to send messages in the specific text channels
2.`Manage Roles` : This is given for role react posts functionallity
2.`Add Reactions` : This is also given for role react posts
3.`Manage Messages` : This is given to remove role react emoji for single react posts
4.`Embed Links` : This is required for embed messages and links used by bot in its messages
5.`Attach Files` : This is required to add files like bday images from server
6.`View Channel` : This is required if you want bot to have access to private channels where it is not added to run commands,but preferably you would want to add bot to any private channel with required perms to work properly
7.`Connect` : For bot to connect to voice channel
8.`Use External Emojis` : Helps improving bot ui with interesting emojis in future
If you face any issues `kick and reinvite` bot or join https://discord.gg/JxS6CB8RWP
